name: Genbu - The Guardian of The North
description:
Genbu, The Dark Warrior, is the guardian of the north. Genbu is one of The Four Protector whose protect the metaverse from four major directions. 
He is associated with the element of water and the color black. He is represented as two creatures, tortoise and snake. 
The tortoise is a symbol of longevity and immortality, while the snake is a symbol of reproduction and multiplication.
Genbu represents a virtue of knowledge, longevity, purity and balance. 

Genbu is the first guardian in the series of 'The Four Protector' by hudxhoods
